data.description: Beautiful home with attention to detail in the desirable Eastmark community. Seller can accommodate a quick closing if  needed! Home is on a great interior lot which looks to the beautiful green park.  Sellers have made this home warm and inviting from the minute you walk in the home.  Notice the detailed wood ceilings at entrance, the custom millwork throughout the main areas!  Fresh paint & new carpet gives the home an upscale feel to this well-maintained home. The kitchen features a large island for meal prep or entertaining, 5 burner gas cooktop, wall ovens, refrigerator and large eat in kitchen.  You'll love the natural light & the double wall sliders which offer indoor outdoor living! Spacious master features large soaking tub, separate large shower, and oversized walk-in closet which opens to the large laundry room! You will love the laundry room great for storage and includes washer and dryer, including cabinets and pre plumbed for a sink.  Beautiful split spacious bedrooms with large walk-in closets. Large secondary bathroom with double sinks. The office is currently set up as a guest room as sellers have just completed having the new barn door installed for privacy.  It can also be used as a second family room if needed!  Beautiful powder bath for guest to enjoy while entertaining.  Out back you will love the covered patio with a new ceiling fan just wired in and installed to give a nice feel to the patio.  The swimming pool is inviting and ready to enjoy! Green turf and pavers make this professionally designed backyard the place to hang out.  The sellers have recently had a professional HVAC move the AC unit to the side of the home which is around the corner to give more space by the pool and a more aesthetic look, it also made the HVAC less noisy when it runs out by the pool and dining areas.  You will love the attention to design elements that the sellers just created for them to enjoy for years.  As they just finished these amazing finishes, they are now being relocated to be with family out of state.  Enjoy all that Eastmark has to offer from the community pool and spa to the green parks throughout and it's a great place to meet new friends and socialize! It's close to the 202 with great shopping, entertainment and dining nearby.  Top-Rated Eastmark Master Plan Community: Situated within Eastmark you'll be sure to enjoy  luxurious living but also access to top-rated schools, the Great Park, community events, food trucks and an array of recreational amenities including a Fishing Lake, Walking Trail, Exercise Court, Community Pool & Shaded Splashpad, Basketball, Baseball & Sand Volleyball Courts, Skate Park, Dog Park as well as Picnic & BBQ Ramadas that can be reserved for your Event. Discover the perfect union of luxury, technology, and space in this exceptional home within the prestigious Eastmark Master Plan community just off the 24 Frwy at Ellsworth.
